      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>These sealed and pressurized glass tubes are filled with a substance derived from dycepskian spores. Each can be used only once. When a fungal bomb explodes, it releases a cloud of modified spores in a 20-foot-radius spread. This is a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JaRMioj4isNp7r1P.JournalEntryPage.gBhZDjh30JEyh7DY]{Disease} effect. Creatures in this area must succeed at a Fortitude save or be @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.ZacF0l6IwqBwToTJ]{Sickened} for 1 day. If a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.ZacF0l6IwqBwToTJ]{Sickened} creature spends Resolve to recover Stamina Points, it can attempt this saving throw again, ending the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.ZacF0l6IwqBwToTJ]{Sickened} condition on a success.</p>"
